description:
Introducing SPHGR: a unified method of analyzing cosmological SPH simulations in yt.  This module groups particles into halos and galaxies providing a simple and intuitive way to work with your data.  We hope to eventually extend this to grid codes as well.  

Documentation is currently lacking, but examples are provided in the /examples folder.  A slightly more in depth introduction on the installation/running/and usage can be found here:

http://rthompsonj.github.io/yt-sphgr.html
title: [WIP] SPHGR
